Codex changes log

- Initialized tracking file.
- Added TaskCoordinator cleanup for callback maps and periodic task queue cleanup.
- Capped background scan results in useNewContentScanner to limit memory growth.
- Capped board background image sizing to reduce large image memory usage.
- Added profile document size limit with per-field error messaging.
- Lazy-load Trello cover images by deferring cover URL population until task open.
- Disabled dev sourcemaps in Vite and lazy-loaded background thumbnails.
- Use smaller thumbnails for workspace/background pickers to reduce image memory.
- Moved task/profile/trello types into src/types and wired imports.
- Extracted Profile view into src/components/ProfileView.tsx and wired App.tsx.
- Extracted Trello parsing into src/features/trelloImport.ts and simplified App.tsx import flow.
- Fixed build issues after refactor; npm run build now passes.
